From daily commutes to spontaneous weekend getaways, choose the ride that fits your needs. With multiple services including tuk-tuk rides, taxi pooling, and private rentals, Ryde Go brings you a smarter way to travel.

Fast, hassle-free ride booking
Affordable taxi and TukTuk rides
Intercity travel for long-distance trips

Car rental service for flexible mobility

Whether you're riding solo or sharing the journey, Ryde Go puts you in control of how you move.

Download Ryde Go now – and ride your way, the new way.

description:
HiWatchPro是一款基于蓝牙手环开发的app，使用蓝牙4.0通信，里面包统计睡眠、遥控拍照(通过手环拍照)，闹钟设置，久坐提醒（设置提醒时间防止用户坐太久），抬手亮屏、计步、消息推送、勿扰模式、睡眠监测、找手环等功能。用户可以利用app直观的了解身体状况以及运动状况，是一款轻量型助手型工具类app。


注意事项：
1，运动功能会使用GPS定位，在后台持续运行GPS功能可能会大幅消耗电池电量
2，HiWatchPro已接入HealthKit，可同步运行数据到健康
3，HiWatchPro所产生的一切数据，仅用于参考，不能当作健康状况依据。

Turn your free time into real rewards by sharing your opinion! With our app you can participate in paid surveys and questionnaires on a wide variety of topics: technology, fashion, entertainment, sports, health, travel, food, current trends, and much more. Every answer you give is valuable, because companies and organizations around the world use this information to improve their products, services, and future decisions. Your opinion matters — and now it can also help you earn real rewards.

Why choose our surveys app? Because it combines the best of usability, rewards, and trust. Unlike other platforms that feel complicated or unreliable, here you will find a clear and intuitive experience from the very first moment. In just a few taps you can start answering surveys that are tailored to your interests, and every completed questionnaire brings you closer to redeeming rewards such as cash, PayPal payments, or gift cards from your favorite stores. 

Main Features:

● Personalized Surveys – Get access to questionnaires designed around your profile and preferences. If you love technology, you’ll receive tech-related surveys. If you’re into lifestyle or entertainment, you’ll see more questions in those categories. This personalization means your experience is always relevant and engaging.  
● Earn Real Rewards – Your time is valuable. That’s why every completed survey gives you points that you can redeem for real-world rewards. Choose between cash, PayPal, or popular gift cards to make the most of your participation.  
● Simple and Intuitive – No complicated menus or long registrations. The app is designed to be easy for everyone, so you can focus on giving your opinion without distractions.  
● Security and Privacy – Your personal data is protected and used only anonymously. Companies see aggregated information, never your identity. We respect your privacy as much as we value your input.  
● Make an Impact – Your answers are more than just data. They help brands, startups, and organizations understand what consumers really want. This way, you’re contributing to better products and services that improve everyday life.  
● Wide Variety of Topics – From new apps and gadgets to lifestyle, health, sports, or even global issues, you’ll always find fresh and interesting surveys waiting for you.  

With our app, you’re not just filling in questionnaires: you’re becoming part of a global community of opinion leaders. Millions of people worldwide are already using surveys to shape the future of the products and services they use every day. Now it’s your turn to join them.

Getting started is simple: download the app, and start answering your first survey today. The more you participate, the faster you’ll accumulate points and the sooner you’ll redeem your rewards. Whether you want a little extra pocket money, a PayPal transfer, or a gift card for shopping online, this app gives you the flexibility to choose what suits you best.

Don’t let your opinions go unheard. Start turning them into rewards right now. By using our app, you’re not only helping brands improve, but also enjoying tangible benefits in return. The combination of simplicity, security, and real payouts makes it the ideal platform for anyone who wants to make the most of their time.  

Download now, join the community, and discover how easy it is to earn money and rewards simply by answering surveys. Your opinion is powerful — let it work for you!

I Am Sober is more than just a free sobriety counter app.

Along with tracking your sober days, it helps you build new habits and provides ongoing motivation by connecting you to a wide network of people all striving for the same goal: staying sober one day at a time.

Through our growing sober community you can learn from others and contribute by sharing insights and tactics that have worked for you.

**The I Am Sober app features:**

• Sober day tracker
To visualize how long you’ve been sober.

• Remember why you quit
Add reasons and photos to help you remember why you want to quit your addiction and stay sober.

• Daily pledge tracker
Take a pledge every day. Sobriety is a 24-hour struggle, so start your day off by making a pledge to stay sober. Then you can review how your day went and log notes at the end of the day.

• Sobriety calculator
View how much money & time you’ve saved by being sober.

• Analyze triggers
Recap each day and find patterns that made your day easier or more challenging than the last.

• Share your story
Either with others or for yourself, take photos and journal your progress directly in the app. Then choose to share it or save it as a reminder for yourself.

• Milestone tracker
Track and celebrate your milestones from 1 day, to 1 week, to 1 month and beyond. Compare experiences with others on their sober journey. Read how they felt at this milestone and what you can expect. If you’re struggling, share your story and invite others to offer help or advice.

• Withdrawal timeline
When you create an account and declare your addiction, you can instantly see a withdrawal timeline to get an idea of what to expect for your next few days (and weeks). What’s more, you can contribute to it. See how many others saw an increase in their restfulness vs those that saw an increase in anxiety. Prepare yourself for what’s to come in recovery.

• Customize your experience
You set the time, your sober birthday, the category of motivation you need, the addictions you’re trying to break, even the end-of-day summaries. Make the app customized to your lifestyle and tailored to your needs.

**Sober Plus subscriptions**

I Am Sober is free to use, but you can support development of the app with a subscription to Sober Plus. With Sober Plus, you'll get access to these premium features:

• Create a group
Stay accountable together and track your sobriety privately. Groups are great for complimenting your real-world group like Alcoholics Anonymous, NA, SA, SMART Recovery, or your rehab center.

• Locked access
Keep your trackers private with a lock that you can access via TouchID or FaceID.

• Data Backups
Save your progress in the cloud and restore your trackers if you get a new device.

• More tracking
Track more addictions and get access to more communities. Even if your addiction is specific like Wine, Online Shopping, or Skin Picking, you’ll find a variety of communities of people who are all trying to get sober from alcohol, drugs, eating disorders, self-harm, and more.
